                  "name": "Tab row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "What's Included",
                    "content": "<ul><li><strong>40oz Glass:</strong> Bamboo lid with silicone seal + glass straw + plastic straw + straw cleaner</li><li><strong>40oz Plastic:</strong> Plastic dishwasher-safe lid + plastic straw</li><li><strong>32oz Glass:</strong> Bamboo lid with silicone seal + straw</li></ul>",
